<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692814>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Coryssiphus spp., male habitus. A. C. praeustus, NMSA 18885. B. C. cinerascens, RMCA 174995. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10692814/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692816>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Leg spination schematics. A. Legend; B. Coryssiphus praeustus, male holotype; C. C. praeustus, female, RMCA 131898; D. Same, RMCA 247653; E. C. cinerascens, male holotype; F. C. unicolor, female holotype = C. cinerascens; G. C. cinerascens, RMCA 131824." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10692816/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692818>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Coryssiphus praeustus, male holotype (A–C, E, I), male NMSA 18885 (D, F–H). A. Dorsal; B. Ventral; C. Left palp, left to right: prolateral, ventral, retrolateral; D. Eye region, do; E. Label; F. Endites, ventral; G. Spinnerets, caudal; H. Spinnerets, ventrocaudal; I Leg IV, tarsal claw. Scale bars: A, B, F: 1 mm; C, D, G, H: 250 µm; I: 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10692818/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692820>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Coryssiphus praeustus, male holotype (A, B, F), female RMCA 131898A (C), male NMSA 18885 (D, E). A. Palp, ventral; B. Palp, retrolateral; C. Epigyne; D. Spinnerets, ventral; E. Chelicerae, ventrolateral; F. Eye region, frontal. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10692820/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692822>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Coryssiphus cinerascens, male holotype (A–C, E), male RMCA 174990 (D). A. Dorsal view; B. Ventral view; C. Left palp, left to right: prolateral, ventral, retrolateral; D. Palp and retrocoxal hymen (arrow); E. Label. Scale bars: A, B: 1 mm; C, D: 250 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10692822/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692826>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. A, B. Coryssiphus praeustus, female RMCA 131898 (A), female RMCA 247653 (B, left), female RMCA 131872 (B, right). C–E. C. cinerascens, female RMCA 177006 (C, left), C. unicolor, holotype (C, right), male holotype (D), female RMCA 131824 (e). A. Vulva, dorsal; B, C. Epigynes. D. palp, ventral (left) and retrolateral (right). E. Vulva, dorsal. Scale bars: A, E: 100 µm; B, C: 250 µm; D: 0.5 mm. Abbreviations: ID, Insemination duct; Sss, Sickle-shaped sclerite; ST1, Spermatheca 1; ST2, Spermatheca 2 (“bursa”)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10692826/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10692828>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Coryssiphus praeustus, female RMCA 131898 (A, B, D, E), RMCA 131898a, b, c (C, top left, middle, right), RMCA 247653 (C, bottom left), RMCA 131872 (C, bottom middle), NCA 2011/886 (C, bottom right). A. Dorsal; B. ventral; C. Epigynes; D. Right chelicera, ventral; E. Vulva, dorsal. Scale bars: A, B: 1 mm; C–E: 250 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10692828/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

